overview: David “Pussyman” Christopher brings another trio of tasty young treats over to his place for some more ‘auditions’ for roles in his main series. Crystal Gold’s a leggy, fake-breasted stripper who shows plenty of passion while she’s enjoying a four-on-the-floor tryst. Light-skinned black beauty Taboo shows off a real flair for oral heat in the build-up to her fiery tussle. And Marine Cartier’s a lean and mean sexual machine whose all-natural figure and undeniably sexual nature drive her segment into the sexual stratosphere. Marine’s an exotic-looking stunner who’s obviously never run into a sexual situation she couldn’t master, and her scene stands as the hottest in this latest no-nonsense collection.
title: Pussyman Auditions 9
